Candle Light Dinner in Bangalore

Hello there, lovebirds and celebration enthusiasts! If you’re looking to experience the best candle light dinner in Bangalore, then you've just struck gold! Area83 is not just another resort—it's a slice of paradise on Bannerghatta Road. With lush greenery, a beautiful lake, and a serene atmosphere, we provide an unparalleled dining experience. Here’s why we’re the talk of the town!

What is a Candle Light Dinner?

The idea of a candle light dinner has captivated romantic souls for ages. Imagine a table set for two, adorned with sparkling silverware, a sumptuous feast, and of course, candles that lend a warm, soft glow to your loved one's face. It’s not just a meal; it's an experience, an intimate occasion that lets you bond, talk, and create beautiful memories.

Why is Area83 the Best Place for a Candle Light Dinner in Bangalore?

Not to toot our own horn, but we do offer the best candle light dinner in Bangalore. Why, you ask? For starters, Area83 is spread across 11 acres of land, with 90% of it being pristine greenery. But what takes the cake is our 18-acre private lake, right beside which you can have your dreamy dinner. Imagine dining in the warm glow of candles, with the tranquil lake waters as your backdrop. It's not just romantic; it's magical!

Unique Features That Make Area83 Stand Out

Our unique landscape is not the only thing that sets us apart. We have a lakeside restaurant that offers exquisite cuisine, from local delicacies to international favorites. The dine-in experience here is like no other, making us one of the most sought-after romantic restaurants in Bangalore.

If you're concerned about privacy, worry not! We offer private candle light dinner settings where it’s just you, your loved one, and the sprawling beauty of nature. The privacy we offer makes your special moments even more memorable.

How to Book a Candle Light Dinner at Area83?

Booking with us is as easy as pie! Just submit the enquiry form or call us directly to check for available slots. Once you decide on the date, you can choose your preferred settings and menus. Curious about the cost? Our candle light dinner Bangalore with price details vary on weekends and normal days. Contact us to know the exact details.

What Makes a Good Candle Light Dinner?

Creating a romantic atmosphere is just one part of a good candle light dinner. Excellent food is a must! Our chefs go the extra mile to cater to your culinary desires. Also, the ambiance should be spot-on; no detail is too small, whether it’s the arrangement of candles, the background music, or even the flowers adorning your table.

Why Choose a Lakeside Setting?

Imagine the gentle evening breeze from the lake caressing your face as you dine by its shores. The calm waters of our 18-acre private lake provide the perfect setting for a romantic candle light dinner in Bangalore. It's not just a meal; it's an experience that you will cherish forever. Let us make your special occasion even more memorable with a breathtaking view of the lake and a custom-crafted menu. Book your table with us today!

Events and Special Occasions

Area83 is not just for couples. Are you looking to celebrate an anniversary, a birthday, or even a milestone achievement? We've got you covered! Our place is one of the best date places in Bangalore for all sorts of occasions. You can even customize your experience to suit your special day.

The Menu That Speaks Volumes

Worried about food choices? Look no further! Our lakeside restaurant prides itself on offering a vast menu that will not only satisfy your hunger but also leave a lasting impression on your palate. Our chefs are masters at crafting a variety of dishes, embracing the rich diversity of Indian cuisine. Whether you're a fan of spicy North-Indian curries or prefer the subtle, comforting flavors of South-Indian food, we have something for you.

And it doesn’t stop at Indian cuisine! Our menu also features an exotic range of continental dishes. From Italian pastas to French desserts, your taste buds are in for a world tour. But we understand that a candle light dinner is about more than just eating; it's an experience. Hence, our menu is meticulously designed to complement the romantic ambiance. Imagine enjoying a succulent steak or a creamy paneer tikka while surrounded by candles and a mesmerizing lake view. It's not just a meal; it’s an adventure for your taste buds and a feast for your eyes.

Candle Light Dinner Restaurants in Bangalore Vs. Area83

While there are many candle light dinner restaurants in Bangalore, what sets us apart is the unique, natural setting we offer. We don't just provide a meal; we offer an unparalleled experience that you would be hard-pressed to find anywhere else. That's why we're not just another date place in Bangalore; we're the destination.

Safety Measures We Follow

We understand that safety is a priority, especially in these trying times. Rest assured, we adhere to all the guidelines and regulations to ensure you have a safe yet enjoyable experience.

Accessibility and Location

Worried about the commute? Our resort is conveniently located on Bannerghatta Road, making it easily accessible. So if you’re searching for a "candle light dinner in Bangalore near me," Area83 should top your list!

In summary, Area83 is not just a resort; it’s a sanctuary where love and celebration find a natural home. Come and experience the best private candle light dinner in Bangalore that you’ll remember for a lifetime.

We’re excited to host you soon. Reserve your table now and make memories that will last forever!

For inquiries and bookings, feel free to contact us. We're here to make your dream date come true!
